text: To being this chip with php tunes is great my truck is stock with the bare minimum dont exhaust gages and diy intake its geared 3:55 with 35's and before the chip it couldnt get out of its own way now its night and day difference 65 daily is great and the 80 daily is strong dont blow much smoke but oh well im ok with that if you are looking for a good cheap power adder this is it great job
